Spacey Spitz:  I am horrified that you do not want to talk to me because of my lack of knowledge about your postings and the purpose of this site... or the Viet Nam War. I must apologize.  I studied your postings carefully and surmised that you are an idot.  How careless of me!  You are an imbecile and an idot.<br>
In reading the title of this site I gathered that it was a site dedicated to the ridicule of a heroic draft card burner with an ostentatious title of &quot;Doc.&quot;  Forgive me, I truthfully believed that this site was to expound, along with others, upon what a pitiful jerk you appear to be.<br>
Please try and understand that lack of knowledge about war stems from the fact that I only served two combat tours in Viet Nam.  I realize that first hand experience in Viet Nam comes no where near the expertise that you gained from watching the six o'clock news.<br>
I am impressed that you can write without using filthy words but still I am perplexed that you write so diligently to document your stupidity rather than let the world wonder about it.
